world file tags definition

[world]
author
name
terrains		number of terrain definions in this file
resources		number of resource definions in this file
bobs			number of bob definions in this file

[terrain_x]
name
texture		texture for this terrain [TODO: anim?]
heightmin		minimum height for this terrain
heightmax		maximum height for this terrain
resources		comma-seperated list of resource names allowed on this terrain

[resource_x]
name
occurence		standard occurence of this resource for a map

[bob_x]
name
resource		resource this bob contains
stock			amount of resources in this bob
heir			bob this bob will be when it dies
anim			anim for this bob
animkey		key for animation; can be "time" or "stock"
animfactor		animation speed